Achievements.Name: Flawless Lap
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the driver(s) who finish a lap with no time penalty against an opponent.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Race
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the driver(s) who finish the race with no time penalty against an opponent.

Achievements.Name: Natural
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the single driver who wins the race with all Assists turned off.

Achievements.Name: Hardcore
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the single driver who wins the race with full Difficulty, including no Assists.

Achievements.Name: Underdog
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the driver who wins the race with a car in the lowest PI of the field.

Achievements.Name: Blowout
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the driver who wins the race, beating the rest of the field by a full race section.

Achievements.Name: Crushing Victory
Achievements.Description: Awarded to any driver who finishes the race with a lapped opponent.

Achievements.Name: Hard Charger
Achievements.Description: Awarded to the driver who starts in 8th place and comes in 1st place.
